      "body": "Hello Study Group,\n\nI hope this email finds everyone well! As we prepare for the next study session, I wanted to share a proposed agenda to ensure that we make the most out of our time together. Please feel free to share any suggestions or additions you might have.\n\n**Proposed Agenda:**\n1. **10:00 AM - 10:15 AM:** Welcome and quick review of key concepts from the last session.\n2. **10:15 AM - 11:00 AM:** Group problem-solving for the upcoming assignment.\n3. **11:00 AM - 11:15 AM:** Short coffee break.\n4. **11:15 AM - 12:00 PM:** Discussion on readings and clarifying doubts.\n5. **12:00 PM - 12:15 PM:** Summary of the session and action items for the next meeting.\n\nThe session will be held in our usual location at the library study room. Please make sure to bring any materials you think will be helpful, like notes, textbooks, or laptops.\n\nLet me know if there's anything specific you'd like us to add to the agenda or discuss during the session.\n\nLooking forward to seeing everyone there!\n\nBest regards,  \nJane Doe  \n"
